column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,s. zErr as errredshift, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, f.z, f.zErr, GN.distance FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#.,#, #) AS GN on p.objid = GN.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = GN.objid join Photoz as f ON f.objid = GN.objid
